SDG 5: Gender Equality

Proportion of Women in Middle or Senior Management (2000-2023)

This map visualizes the percentage change of women in middle or senior management positions across Europe. The change has been calculated by grouping the data into two bins (2000-2010 and 2013-2023). The average values has been calculated for both bins and then the avg. values are compared with each other. Based on the improvement or decline of those two values, the data is labeled. By hovering over a country you can get a first glance of its percentange change and by clicking on it a popup with additional information will appear.

Data Source: United Nations unstats.un.org
